Package: DBopen
Type: Package
Title: Query the DB-Open-Data timetable API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Philipp", "Ottolinger", email = "philipp@ottolinger.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Philipp Ottolinger <philipp@ottolinger.de>
Description: This package offers a few functions to query the DB-Open-Data timetable API. It offers functionality to fetch departure and arrival boards as well as fetching more detailed information on specific trains.
License: GPL-3
